<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body>
    <div class="animsition">
      <p>Welcome : <span> {{name}} </span></p>
      <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn cyan"
        href="/logout/facebook">Logout</a>
      <div class="container center" id="cofeeShop">
        <h5 class="center">We Are Doing Business Here & BTW We’ll Learn Accounting Too</h5>
        <br>
        <p>Choose what type of business you’d like to start up … </p>
        <div class="row row-box">
          <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn box cyan"
              id="cs-btn">CofeeShop</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn box cyan disabled">Foto Studio</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn box cyan disabled">Smoothie Stall</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container hidin" id="cofeeShop-wel">
        <h5>Great You’ve Chosen a Coffee Shop business, Let’s start…  </h5>
        <br>
        <h6>Now think about every thing you need to start up this business ‘be
              creative make it your own’</h6>
        <br>
        <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn cyan" id="goAhead">Go Ahead</a>
      </div>

      <div class="container hidin" id="cofeeShop-info">
        <h5>Let’s Talk Business, Shall we? </h5>
        <br>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col s12">
                What is the name of your coffee shop?
                <div class="input-field inline">
                  <input id="name" type="name" class="validate">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col s12">
                Are you buying the shop or renting it?
                <div class="input-field inline">
                  <select>
                    <option value="1">Buying</option>
                    <option value="2">Renting</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <br>
          <li>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col s12">
                What do you need to have (buy) to start up the business?
                <table class="responsive-table striped">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Coffee machine </td>
                      <td>$300</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Van </td>
                      <td>$8000</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Furniture</td>
                      <td>$5000</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <br>
          <li>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col s12">
                Where are you going to raise the money from?
                <br>
                <table class="responsive-table striped">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Personal Savings</td>
                      <td>$0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Credit card</td>
                      <td>$0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>Family borrowing</td>
                      <td>$0</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn cyan" id="goInfo">Go Info</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
